text: Moin Uddin Bhuiyan is a Bangladeshi Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Narsingdi-5. ==Career== Bhuiyan was elected to parliament from Narsingdi-5 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Moin Uddin Bhuiyan
